  "name": "RPlog_A_Gathering_of_Shadows",
  "title": "A Gathering of Shadows",
  "summary": "In the notorious Meltdown Cafe on Nar Shaddaa, the Twi'lek Karawn'Rai and his chain-smoking partner Torin wait over drinks and tabac for the rest of a newly assembled crew. They are joined by the Quarren Korlen and then by their employer, the smuggler Jaspar, captain of the freighter Hirakiis and head of Andromidas Galaxy Logistics. Over rounds of drinks bought on Jaspar's tab, he lays out the operation: mostly clean, above-board transport jobs, with the occasional dirty run smuggling glitterstim and ryll-spice disguised as medical cargo, all while avoiding Caspian space and Imperial checkpoints. The crew sort out their specialties -- Karawn at hiding goods, Torin with chemicals and a possible onboard lab, Korlen with computers and security -- and trade jokes about bunks, bed lice, and Jaspar's Imperial-inflicted prosthetic hand. The meeting ends amiably with the crew agreeing to terms, Jaspar providing a weapons contact to replace Korlen's lost blaster, and everyone drifting off, partnership sealed.",
